sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Envoy as Envoy Gateway<br/>80/TCP HTTP
    participant EPP as EPP (Endpoint Picker)<br/>9002/TCP gRPC
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant ZMQ as vLLM KV Events<br/>5556/TCP ZMQ
    participant Tokenizer as UDS Tokenizer<br/>Unix Socket
    participant Sidecar as Routing Sidecar<br/>8000/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Prefiller as vLLM Prefiller<br/>(remote)
    participant Decoder as vLLM Decoder<br/>8001/TCP (local)

    Note over EPP,K8sAPI: Flow 1: Inference Request Routing (EPP)

    EPP->>K8sAPI: Watch InferencePool CRs & Pods<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token
    EPP->>ZMQ: Subscribe KV-cache events<br/>ZMQ SUB/5556

    Client->>Envoy: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP/80
    Envoy->>EPP: ext-proc ProcessingRequest<br/>gRPC/9002 (request headers)
    EPP->>Tokenizer: Tokenize prompt<br/>Unix Socket
    Tokenizer-->>EPP: Token IDs
    Note over EPP: Run filter chain:<br/>by-label, by-label-selector,<br/>decode-filter, roles-filter
    Note over EPP: Run scorers:<br/>prefix-cache, session-affinity,<br/>load-aware, active-request
    EPP-->>Envoy: ProcessingResponse<br/>Selected endpoint + headers
    Envoy->>Decoder: Forward to selected vLLM pod<br/>HTTP/varies

    Note over Sidecar,Decoder: Flow 2: Disaggregated P/D Inference (NIXL v2)

    Envoy->>Sidecar: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP(S)/8000
    Note over Sidecar: Parse x-prefill-target header<br/>Validate against SSRF allowlist
    Sidecar->>Prefiller: Clone request to prefiller<br/>HTTP(S)/varies
    Prefiller-->>Sidecar: Response with kv_transfer_params<br/>(KV block metadata)
    Note over Sidecar: Inject kv_transfer_params<br/>into decode request body
    Sidecar->>Decoder: Forward to local decoder<br/>HTTP/8001 (with KV params)
    Decoder-->>Sidecar: Inference response<br/>(streaming or non-streaming)
    Sidecar-->>Envoy: Forward response to client

    Note over Sidecar,Decoder: Flow 3: E/P/D Multimodal Inference

    Envoy->>Sidecar: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP(S)/8000 (with images/audio)
    Note over Sidecar: Detect multimodal content
    par Concurrent Encoder Fanout
        Sidecar->>Prefiller: Encode stage 1<br/>HTTP(S)/varies
        Sidecar->>Prefiller: Encode stage N<br/>HTTP(S)/varies
    end
    Sidecar->>Prefiller: Prefill stage<br/>HTTP(S)/varies (after encode)
    Prefiller-->>Sidecar: kv_transfer_params
    Sidecar->>Decoder: Decode with KV params<br/>HTTP/8001
    Decoder-->>Sidecar: Inference response
    Sidecar-->>Envoy: Forward response
